00:05:33,963 --> 00:05:37,633
So $425,000 of
your $525,000 in revenue

00:05:37,633 --> 00:05:38,434
is from a sponsor?

00:05:38,434 --> 00:05:41,370
We have to walk a fine line
between sales and sponsorship,

00:05:41,370 --> 00:05:43,973
because we--our sponsors
are sponsoring us

00:05:43,973 --> 00:05:45,174
to play for free.

00:05:45,174 --> 00:05:47,310
