"can you put out some books--"

00:05:56,252 --> 00:05:57,853
you're dancing
around the question.

00:05:57,853 --> 00:05:59,188
Give me one advantage--
Let me be clear on this--

00:05:59,188 --> 00:06:01,257
the answer is,
at baby loves disco,

00:06:01,257 --> 00:06:01,857
we make money
from sponsorship,

00:06:01,857 --> 00:06:03,793
we make money
from ticket sales,

00:06:03,793 --> 00:06:05,861
and we make money
from merchandise.

00:06:05,861 --> 00:06:07,763
Give me an event,
just one Saturday afternoon.

00:06:07,763 --> 00:06:09,432
How much money do I make?

00:06:09,432 --> 00:06:11,767
We make
between $1,500 and $3,000

00:06:11,767 --> 00:06:13,169
on each individual event.

00:06:13,169 --> 00:06:14,770
How much will
the sales be next year?

00:06:14,770 --> 00:06:18,708
Next year, we're projecting
to make $750,000.

00:06:18,708 --> 00:06:19,642
What amount will come
from the shows,

00:06:19,642 --> 00:06:22,978
from sponsorship,
from the merchandise?

00:06:22,978 --> 00:06:25,247
Well, merchandise
is a question mark,

